io.realm.log

Interface Logger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndroidLogger
    Deprecated. 
    Use RealmLogger instead.

    public interface Logger
    Interface for custom loggers that can be registered at RealmLog.add(Logger). The different log levels are described in LogLevel.

    • Method Detail

      • getMinimumNativeDebugLevel

        int getMinimumNativeDebugLevel()
        Deprecated. 
        Defines which LogLevel events this logger cares about from the native components.

        If multiple loggers are registered, the minimum value among all loggers is used.

        Note that sending log events from the native layer is relatively expensive, so only set this value to events that are truly useful.

        Returns:
        the minimum LogLevel native events this logger cares about.
